Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:25.23,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Dare wo matteruno?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:27.02,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Shiroi nooto ni tsuzutta youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:28.77,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Motto sunao ni hakidashitai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:30.44,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Nani kara nogaretainda
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:32.07,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Genjitsu tte yatsu?
